Inclusion Criteria:

1. planned treatment and follow-up within the NM or UHealth healthcare system;
2. ≥ 18 years of age;
3. medical chart confirmed diagnosis of a solid or hematological malignancy;
4. elevated depressive symptoms on the PROMIS CAT (score \> or = 55) within the last 3 months;
5. access to the internet;
6. willingness to be randomized;
7. able to read English or Spanish;
8. patients must have signed informed consent prior to registration on study

Exclusion Criteria:

Note: The investigators will not include any vulnerable populations in this study.
